05:45.244 --> 05:48.907
Now, I don't know if this
is your department or not.

05:49.082 --> 05:52.415
Justin Pitt, this is Elaine Benes.

05:59.025 --> 06:00.583
Charmed.

06:01.260 --> 06:06.254
I was a great admirer
of Mrs. Onassis.

06:08.634 --> 06:11.933
Hello, Karen?
Hi, it's Jerry Seinfeld.

06:12.105 --> 06:13.868
Oh, that's very sweet of you.

06:14.040 --> 06:16.565
You better be careful.
You don't wanna get too congenial.

06:16.743 --> 06:19.143
They'll slap that
Miss Congeniality on you...

06:19.312 --> 06:22.713
...you'll congenial yourself
right out of the contest.

06:24.384 --> 06:27.182
So, what time
you wanna get together later?

06:27.587 --> 06:28.986
What?

06:29.155 --> 06:31.089
So what?
We don't need the chaperone.

06:31.257 --> 06:32.485
Her chaperone can't make it.

06:33.826 --> 06:36.761
Oh, you're not
gonna get disqualified.

06:36.929 --> 06:38.954
So we're not going?

06:39.866 --> 06:42.061
Come on.
Hold on one second.

06:42.235 --> 06:44.567
-Hey, what are you doing tonight?
-Nothing.

06:45.671 --> 06:48.299
I'm going out with a Miss America
contestant. You wanna go?

06:48.474 --> 06:50.669
What state?

06:54.180 --> 06:55.442
Rhode Island.

06:55.615 --> 06:57.412
They're never in contention.

06:58.651 --> 06:59.982
How do you know?

07:00.153 --> 07:03.179
Because I've seen every
Miss America pageant since I was 6.

07:03.356 --> 07:05.415
Do you wanna go or not?
I'll buy you dinner.

07:05.591 --> 07:08.253
-Giddyup.
