have brown eyes.

07:25.278 --> 07:30.079
No, there's something else.
An indefinable quality.

07:30.483 --> 07:32.383
Grace?

07:32.885 --> 07:34.216
Grace, yes.

07:35.121 --> 07:37.453
You think I have grace?

07:38.024 --> 07:40.993
-Some grace, yes.
-Just some?

07:41.160 --> 07:44.129
Well, you don't want too much grace,
or you won't be able to stand.

07:48.034 --> 07:50.059
Oh, Mr. Pitt.

07:51.204 --> 07:55.800
Elaine, I want you to come and work
for me as my personal assistant.

07:55.975 --> 07:58.136
Now, I'll pay you the same
as Pendant...

07:58.311 --> 08:01.246
...but I would need you
to start right away.

08:05.518 --> 08:08.009
Hey, Buck.
Talk to you for a second?

08:08.187 --> 08:10.212
Sure, George.

08:10.389 --> 08:12.357
How's everything going?
Everything okay?

08:12.525 --> 08:15.983
Well, all of a sudden, there's a
problem with Tartabull's swing, but...

08:18.431 --> 08:21.161
Listen, Buck, obviously
I don't need to talk to you...

08:21.334 --> 08:24.826
...about the importance
of player morale.

08:25.004 --> 08:26.938
But I've been talking
to some of the guys...

08:27.106 --> 08:30.837
...I don't wanna mention any names,
but some of them aren't too happy...

08:31.010 --> 08:33.376
...with the polyester uniforms.

08:33.546 --> 08:37.038
-How so?
-They get very hot in the polyester.

08:37.216 --> 08:39.548
