08:39.719 --> 08:42.210
I think they would prefer cotton.

08:43.256 --> 08:46.089
-Cotton, huh?
-Cotton breathes.

08:46.259 --> 08:48.352
See, it's much softer.

08:48.528 --> 08:49.825
Imagine playing games...

08:49.996 --> 08:52.521
