09:20.393 --> 09:23.419
Well, like tomorrow,
for example, l...

09:23.829 --> 09:27.287
-I have to buy him some socks.
-Really?

09:27.466 --> 09:29.457
-Socks.
-Yeah.

09:29.635 --> 09:31.626
White ones.
The ones you wear with sneakers.

09:31.804 --> 09:33.635
