-lf you think I'm gonna step aside...

09:52.725 --> 09:54.989
...while you defile this woman,
you're crazy.

09:55.161 --> 09:57.356
I'm not going to defile her.

09:57.530 --> 09:59.760
Right, because I'm gonna see
it doesn't happen.

09:59.932 --> 10:01.866
These girls are
Miss America contestants.

10:02.034 --> 10:03.501
It's every little girl's dream.

10:03.669 --> 10:05.534
